The paper discusses probabilistic inference algorithms in distributed systems, which involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and distributed computing (cs.DC). The use of sensor networks and mobile robots also suggests the sub-categories of systems and control (cs.SY), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), and machine learning (cs.LG).
